name: LibraryMusicVideos.Relationships
desc: The relationships from library music videos to other resources.

items.name: albums
items.desc: The library albums associated with the music video. By default, albums not included. Fetch limits: 10 default, 10 maximum.

items.name: artists
items.desc: The library artists associated with the music video. By default, artists not included. Fetch limits: 10 default, 10 maximum.

items.name: catalog
items.desc: The music video in the Apple Music catalog the library music video is associated with, when known.Fetch limits: None (associated with at most one catalog music video).
